Product Support Services









Revenue Analytics Login    Community Login




I’ve got this really cool product – now what?
ServiceSource Customer Care and Training is here to help you achieve the full value of your software investment. Our technical experts and trainers will work with you to ensure you and your teams adopt and fully utilize the software, ultimately helping you achieve your business objectives.



Help on-hand when you need it
From onboarding to ongoing support, ServiceSource is here to help you achieve the full value of your software investment. Our technical experts and trainers will work with you to troubleshoot your issues--and ensure you’re empowered for the long term.




Customer Support
Customer care is an essential part of our partnership. As such, standard support is included with every software subscription. ServiceSource offers online case submission, 8x5 support hours and technical expertise for your Named Support contacts.
Support Terms and Conditions





ServiceSource Customer Community
All the right resources just a click away. Get the answers you need from the ServiceSource Customer Community, a one-stop shop for e-learning, knowledge articles and product announcements. Connect with fellow users to share best practices and submit your recommendations for product enhancements.
Already a Community Member?
 

Community Login





Training
Long-term success begins with a solid foundation. To help you build and sustain competence with our software solutions, ServiceSource offers live online training to cover a range of core concepts and functionality. Our training courses are designed to match your skill, role and schedule.

Basic Product Training

Training Sessions


